    "rationale": "All 13 ASME V&V 40 credibility factors have been reviewed. Seven factors were formally assessed; all seven show achieved levels below required levels for Model Risk Level 5. Six factors remain unassessed and are flagged as epistemic gaps. Monte Carlo UQ was conducted on inlet boundary conditions but does not cover the full uncertain input space. The overall credibility evidence is insufficient to support regulatory submission for the Class III VAD indication. The assessment package itself is accepted as a complete credibility dossier for record; the underlying model is not accepted for the stated COU.",
